message.content: cs.MOBILE, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.SD, cs.SY - The paper focuses on energy efficiency in mobile devices and proposes an approach for energy-aware programming. Therefore, cs.MOBILE is the most likely category. The paper also discusses software optimization and code optimization, which are related to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Additionally, the proposed approach is placed at the end of the software engineering life cycle, which is related to software development (cs.SD) and system design (cs.SY).
